FBIS3-41282 "jptdd007__l94072" JPRS-TDD-94-007-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 14 February 1994 WEST EUROPE GERMANY 90 Kg of Heroin Aboard Turkish Truck Seized at Czech Border AU0802135294 Hamburg DPA in German 1215 GMT 8 Feb 94 AU0802135294 Hamburg DPA Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Nuremberg (DPA) -- At the German-Czech border checkpoint of Furth im Wald-Schafberg police and customs officials seized 90 kg of heroin. The drugs were hidden in a refrigerated truck from Turkey. According to first findings, the cargo was destined for the Netherlands, the joint investigating group of police and customs anounced in Nuremberg on Tuesday.
